{"tid":2450192,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"全球首例！ 美國孕婦打Moderna疫苗 母女同有抗體","createTime":"2021-03-17T08:15:13.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-17T09:28:59.000Z","uid":28114,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d5e9f5538c6bc169bd3afc2099c26948a133fd","tid":2450192,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/news/600/2021/03/17/3469777_1_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fnews%2F600%2F2021%2F03%2F17%2F3469777_1_1.jpg&h=92ef605b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國孕婦於懷孕期間接種武肺疫苗，其後經母體轉移，產下的嬰兒也帶有抗體。示意圖。（路透資料照）<br />\n2021/03/17 14:57<br />\n<br />\n〔編譯陳成良／綜合報導〕以色列初步研究指出，孕婦接種「輝瑞＆BioNTech」武漢肺炎疫苗可提供胎兒防護力，事實上第一名生下來就帶有武肺病毒抗體的「疫苗寳寳」，已經在美國誕生了！<br />\n<br />\n據美國福斯電視台頻道35（FOX35）報導，佛羅里達州一名女醫護於懷孕36週時接種莫德納（Moderna）疫苗，3星期後產下一名也帶有病毒抗體的健康女嬰，成為全球首位經母親接種武肺疫苗而帶武肺病毒抗體的嬰兒。<br />\n<br />\n前線醫護人員是美國首批接種武肺疫苗群體之一。佛州大西洋大學婦產科醫師吉爾伯特（Paul Gilbert）與魯德尼克（Chad Rudnick）撰寫的報告指出，該孕婦接種疫苗第一劑後接受檢測，她體內出現抗體，認為抗體可能透過胎盤，讓胎兒也擁有武肺抵抗力。<br />\n<br />\n相關研究成果發表在醫學論文預印本網站MedRxiv上，往後還將發表於其他正式期刊；論文指出，新生兒懷胎期滿、健康且活力十足。<br />\n<br />\n吉爾伯特醫師指出，就他們所知，孕婦接種武肺疫苗，而生下也有抗體的嬰生，這是世上第一例；不過，目前尚不清楚抗體保護力多強、效力能多久。<br />\n<br />\n2位醫師強調，未來幾個月將有數以萬計的母親接種武肺疫苗，需要更多的研究確定抗體在嬰兒體內持續時間，以及需要多少抗體才能為嬰兒提供保護。<br />\n<br />\n事實上，去年新加坡一項研究顯示，5名孕婦感染武肺病毒後產下的嬰兒，都具有病毒抗體，懷疑由母體轉移。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3469777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3469777&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=9119c911\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3469777&h=d5b697fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3469777</a>"},{"pid":"727bdf68eb01c1cf816a68f1d6797e4a4d7f73ba","tid":2450192,"uid":28114,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:16:42.000Z","msg":"FYI<br />\n<br />\nUS woman gives birth to first known baby with Covid antibodies, doctors say<br />\nThe mother, a frontline healthcare worker, received her first Moderna dose in January, at 36 weeks pregnant<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/mar/16/florida-woman-vaccine-dose-baby-covid-coronavirus-antibodies\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fus-news%2F2021%2Fmar%2F16%2Fflorida-woman-vaccine-dose-baby-covid-coronavirus-antibodies&d=V7AID%2B4Ek1BfB0hSL70CTyukga04qSQtFIF%2FU0RrEoA%3D&h=e952d545\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/us-news/2021/mar/16/florida-woman-vaccine-dose-baby-covid-coronavirus-antibodies</a>"},{"pid":"e454ce9fe7f4f6774d4020ad6a27c0aca691bf66","tid":2450192,"uid":30084,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:17:50.000Z","msg":"優先接種群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4699e58a9f02692e93f5ec4f2cc035529d42b2ef","tid":2450192,"uid":168366,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:18:19.000Z","msg":"To deepstate/陰毛論撚<br />\nAntibody不嬲可以由母親去個B度"},{"pid":"82298ccf2ecdb5fe0cbbfdf413a866f084d76b24","tid":2450192,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e454ce9fe7f4f6774d4020ad6a27c0aca691bf66","tid":2450192,"uid":30084,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:17:50.000Z","msg":"優先接種群組<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"唔係要問咗醫生先接種得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffc9044489c667d0d0d0bec3ddd63447bb5295ad","tid":2450192,"uid":393145,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-17T08:18:37.000Z","msg":"孕婦打科興會..<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3e80dac6efa10defbe1b4c5c7835ddcf3915ec1","tid":2450192,"uid":77196,"like":4,"dislike":0,"scor